Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.51,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切なものを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.98,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}一番大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.57,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな単純なことが今は一番出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.44,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}もしも運命があるのならば　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.16,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「あなたは運命の人」なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.00,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}そんな言葉今を壊しそうで言えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.62,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近くに居ても遠く感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.14,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}行ったり来たりしてるこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.15,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}諦める　諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.30,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}終わらない花占い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.74,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}宝箱の鍵失ったなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.36,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}キラキラした想いて抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:07.90,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}仄かに色付いた欠片をため息に隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.36,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}目が合ったなら逸らさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.94,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}秘められたこの嘘を見抜いてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.42,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}限界がもう分からないの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.21,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}だから今は何も言わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.27,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}苦しいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:37.20,Kuzu_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}怖いほどあなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.51,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最寶貴的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.98,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}最想要去珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.57,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如此簡單的事情現在卻最無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.44,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若是真的存在命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:40.16,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}「你就是我的命定之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.00,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}無法說出口 懼怕這些話語將會毀掉現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:47.62,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}近在咫尺卻彷若遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.14,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}反覆無常的這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.15,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}放棄 還是堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:55.30,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}永無止境的花瓣占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.74,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}若然丟失了寶箱的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:02:00.36,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}抱緊最後一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:07.90,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}將逐漸泛紅的碎片藏進一聲聲嘆息中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:18.36,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}如果看著我 請不要移開目光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.94,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}讓你看透我所隱藏的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:23.42,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}我不知自己能堅持到何時
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.21,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}所以現在請你沉默就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.66,0:02:33.27,Kuzu_opch,NTP,0,0,0,fx,{\blur3}{\fad(150,150)}愛的如此痛苦
